      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 69.9 - 老子 69.10</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 69.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故抗兵相加，哀者勝矣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it is that when opposing weapons are (actually) crossed, he who deplores (the situation) conquers.</seg>
      </tuv>
